    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><rs key="#Offersio/donatio">Donatio</rs> propter nuptias medietatis omnium
                        bonorum suorum provenientium ab <rs key="#Testamentum">hereditate paterna et
                            materna</rs> et unius fratris suis in <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Production">campisque</rs> facta a <persName><name ref="Gaudius"
                                >Gaudio</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes de Monte">Iohannis de Monte</name></persName> favore
                                <persName><name ref="Ermengarda">Hermengardę</name></persName> filie
                                <persName><name ref="Everardus de Firmo">Everardi de
                            Firmo</name></persName> sponsę suę. Actum […], rog. […], 1080, <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/77">Henrici</persName> Henrici filii
                        anno XXIII, 1078, VIII kalendas […], indictione II.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>Mezzetti, <foreign>Le carte</foreign>, vol. 2, doc. 83 (in preparazione).</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
